body: # Brian Cochran ##Biography Brian Cochran Education: Pursuing Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science at Georgia Institute of Technology Interests: Robotics and machine learning Skills: Object-Oriented Programming, 3D CAD Modeling, 3D Printing, CNC Machines Leadership: Wrote curriculum for and taught LEGO Robotics summer camp for middle and high school students; Founder and mentor of two FIRST Robotics Teams Mission Statement: To create technology to better the lives of others and allow others to achieve their goals ##Contact Brian Cochran BCochran32@gatech.edu https://github.com/btdubs
